description: Testing strategy and standards
---

# Testing Standards

All features must include automated tests.

---

## Testing Layers

The system should include:

Unit Tests  
Integration Tests  
End-to-End Tests

---

## Unit Testing

Unit tests must cover:

Domain logic  
Application handlers  
Validation rules

Use:

xUnit  
FluentAssertions  
Moq

---

## Integration Testing

Integration tests verify:

Database access  
API endpoints  
Service interactions

Use test databases when required.

---

## End-to-End Testing

E2E tests validate user workflows.

Use:

Playwright

Example flows:

User login  
Form submission  
Feature workflows

---

## Test Naming

Test names must describe behavior.

Example:

DeactivateUser_ShouldDisableLogin

---

## Test Philosophy

Tests should verify:

Expected behavior  
Edge cases  
Failure scenarios

Avoid fragile tests.